# Place a production database dump here (e.g. mindsuit.sql or mindsuit.sql.gz)
# to seed a fresh MySQL volume on first `make up`.
#
# Dumps are loaded automatically by the MySQL entrypoint, in alphabetical order,
# ONLY when the db_data volume is empty. To re-import after the volume exists:
#   make db-reset
#
# Never commit real customer data dumps to git (this directory is gitignored
# except for this file).
